<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29884>
    dc:description "Figures 24 - 27. Lupaeus illustrations. 24 a Pedipalp tibiotarsus 24 b Genital setae not in a row, g 3 out of line 25 - 27 Lupaeus key illustrations. Setae and cupules removed from figures 25 a, b to increase clairity 25 a Lupaeus longisetus, dorsal 25 b Lupaeus polilloensis, dorsal 26 a Ventral, small platelet present 26 b Ventral, small platelet absent 27 a Setae f 1, f 2 born on small platelets 27 b Setae f 1, f 2 born on integument." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29884" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

